race.description: Nutrien Ag Solutions St Arnaud Handicap
race.comment: TUNDRA (1) was prominent through the early and middle stages but peaked on his run and finished fourth when resuming over 1200m at Murtoa last start. Has the gate speed to take up a forward position. Best form puts him right in this. BROMEO (2) was out of the money when resuming two runs back then again missed the frame last start over 1200m at Wodonga, beaten 4.5 lengths into fourth. Suitably placed so anticipating a big run this time. TIMBOLTON (7) was in the money two starts back at Jerilderie but couldn't back it up last time when eighth at Manangatang over 1550m. Has his share of ability and can do a lot better.
